<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ḥbk yạ yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ḥbk yạ yswʿ gẖyr ḥạly wkẖly̱ ṭʿm ạlʿysẖẗ yḥlạly
 1- kạnt ạ̉ḥmạly tqylẗ ʿly wtḥtạ ktạfy kạnt mḥnyẗ
 wfjạ̉ẗ smʿtk ʿm btqly tʿạ ạ̉ḥmạlk ạ̉nạ ʿnk bdy ạ̹rfʿhạ
 jyt lʿndk fyk lqyt mʿny ạlḥryẗ
 2- ḥbk gẖyr qlby klh mn ạlạ̉sạs msẖ rḥ ạ̹skt bdy kẖbr kl ạlnạs
 ạ̹n dẖnwby ṣạrt mgẖfwrẗ wtḥt ạldm ʿywby mstwrẗ
 wʿndk wḥdk bs lqyt mʿny̱ ạlḥryẗ</lyrics>
